1. *Propustio* je mnoge prilike da ostvari svoje želje. (He missed many opportunities to fulfill his wishes.)
2. Ona je *propustila* šansu da se istakne. (She missed the chance to stand out.)
3. Zbog njegove nepromišljenosti *propustio* ježivotnu priliku. (Because of his thoughtlessness, he missed a lifetime opportunity.)
4. *Propustiti* ćeš mnoge lekcije ako ne budeš marljiv. (You will miss out on many lessons if you are not diligent.)
5. Njegov nedostatak pažnje ga je skupo *koštao*- *propustio* je priliku da postigne svoj cilj. (His lack of attention costed him dearly- he missed the chance to achieve his goal.)